        " set up a commission which ran from 42 till 42 headed by Pothier, and an editorial team, run by Mocquereau, to create official chant editions for the Vatican. Mocquereaus editorial team only lasted a year: owing to editorial disagreements with Mocquereau, Pothier ended up in charge of the editing which, amongst other things, led to the production of a revised ": null
    },
